<div><h3>COMM 1240 - Introduction to Visual Communication </h3>  <hr>Students explore and apply fundamentals in visual communication.  They will learn and practice using various software applications to investigate visual representation of informative and persuasive materials.  Through experiential learning, students will learn to effectively create, present and communicate design solutions and projects. <em>Formally ART 1240</em><br><br><strong>Anticipated Terms Offered:</strong> Varied<br><br></div>		</td>
